{"tid":1623875,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"通識分享 - 禁蒙面法與法治社會","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:34:52.000Z","uid":229880,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27d685d8244634f130fb9989acf3ab8667da51ea","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"兩個月前，講解法治的四個層次給同學聽<br />\n<br />\n﻿想舉一個相對荒謬的例子，怎知這例子成真了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5V3Kma8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5V3Kma8.jpg&h=7c535e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n﻿<br />\n有上過堂嘅同學一定會見過「有法可依、有法必依、以法限權、以法達義」呢16個字。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n以上嘅4個層面，展示法治社會嘅特徵，只要做齊就有助維持社會穩定。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n守法係法治社會嘅其中一個條件，但只係守法唔代表足以做到以法達義、彰顯公義。舉一個較為極端嘅例子，同學就好易明白：﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n「政府為方便執法和檢控，立法禁止所有市民戴上口罩、頭盔、頭巾等可遮蓋容貌的器具。」﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n假設人民懼怕此法，不戴上任何配飾。這是守了法，但絕沒有彰顯法治，更不免限制人生自由，令社會失去多元色彩。因此，要彰顯法治就是要法例本身恰當，或具正當性，符合社會共識，否則只會令一地社會失去可貴的自由，令人活在恐懼之中。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n以上嘅嘢會唔會考？﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n2014年嘅考評報告就曾指：「考生對法治誤解或片面理解為執法或守法，應擴闊及加強法治功能等概念。法治不僅是依法而治，學生須更全面理解公義、尊重個人價值等法治原則⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dselsjohnyy/photos/a.2451063168240543/2820273404652849?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdselsjohnyy%2Fphotos%2Fa.2451063168240543%2F2820273404652849%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFnG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=61a47424\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dselsjohnyy/photos/a.2451063168240543/2820273404652849?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n有興趣嘅同學可以自行去睇返～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會繼續不定期免費網上教通識<br />\n<br />\n香港正經歷艱難時刻，有需要的同學可隨時係度提問<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: 通識5星星<br />\nIg: dse_ls_johnyy"},{"pid":"e48731098524ac6873f38022d33367cebba56caa","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"通識5**分享 完全免費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n之前舊post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef55d0be2821295b7abbdfca7f1a6a6d22a2641","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:37.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"67d9a698db193fa3a4538a960c8caf8a38d0a5a1","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"16b6e4509e5f8df43c10b7d7fb8690e050007963","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"40f9b71265a85da09a153da446043af84aa08de5","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"e43050157fd80e63c5988ad32957580755f33727","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"3e9e458ecd20b88fa24db20302b9e67893251aa4","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"0881dd0a4a5a65511f8274609f03d6310dcd9d1e","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"自推7/10"},{"pid":"2b7b6debcfee21558d5fa17e226d4b2cf44e53de","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"自推8/10"},{"pid":"3f38050954f8b8850f138a35bc6fd9f2d1489e2e","tid":1623875,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:09:46.000Z","msg":"自推9/10"},{"pid":"5609682db095b3675d14d40076467bfc995dec40","tid":1623875,"uid":21641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"re